headline.main: Serbian Court Rejects Extradition of Montenegro Coup Suspect
headline.print_headline: Serbian Court Rejects Extradition of Montenegro Coup Suspect

lead_paragraph: A Serbian court has rejected a second extradition request by Montenegro for suspects in an alleged pro-Russia plot to overthrow the Balkan country's government.
